                    <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/BGRGT37I"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Grebaut1917MiraclesJesusI"/><title level="m">Les miracles de Jésus&lt;hi rend="italics"&gt;, I&lt;/hi&gt;</title><title level="s">Patrologia Orientalis</title><author><forename>Sylvain</forename><surname>Grébaut</surname></author><editor><forename>Sylvain</forename><surname>Grébaut</surname></editor><pubPlace>Paris</pubPlace><publisher>Firmin-Didot et C&lt;sup&gt;ie&lt;/sup&gt;, imprimeurs-éditeurs</publisher><date>1917</date><series><title level="s">Patrologia Orientalis</title><biblScope unit="volume">12/4 (60)</biblScope></series><biblScope unit="volume">12/4 (60)</biblScope><note type="tags"><note type="tag">bm:Grebaut1917MiraclesJesusI</note></note><note type="tag">bm:Grebaut1917MiraclesJesusI</note><citedRange unit="page">558</citedRange></bibl>
                    <ab>
                        ዝንቱ፡ ምሥጢር፡ አምላካዊ፡ ዘነገሮ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ወአምላክነ፡ ወመድኀኒነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ለረድኡ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ ወልደ፡ ዘብዴዎስ፡ እምቅድመ፡ ዕርገቱ፡ ለእግዚእነ፡ ወአምላክነ፡
                        ወመድኀኒነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ውስተ፡ ሰማያት፡ ዘኢተፈልጠ፡ እምአቡሁ፡ ወእመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ አሐተኒ፡ ሰዓተ፡ ወኢከመ፡ ቅጽበተ፡ ዓይን።
                    </ab>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="explicit" xml:lang="gez">
                    <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/BGRGT37I"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Grebaut1917MiraclesJesusI"/><title level="m">Les miracles de Jésus&lt;hi rend="italics"&gt;, I&lt;/hi&gt;</title><title level="s">Patrologia Orientalis</title><author><forename>Sylvain</forename><surname>Grébaut</surname></author><editor><forename>Sylvain</forename><surname>Grébaut</surname></editor><pubPlace>Paris</pubPlace><publisher>Firmin-Didot et C&lt;sup&gt;ie&lt;/sup&gt;, imprimeurs-éditeurs</publisher><date>1917</date><series><title level="s">Patrologia Orientalis</title><biblScope unit="volume">12/4 (60)</biblScope></series><biblScope unit="volume">12/4 (60)</biblScope><note type="tags"><note type="tag">bm:Grebaut1917MiraclesJesusI</note></note><note type="tag">bm:Grebaut1917MiraclesJesusI</note><citedRange unit="page">576</citedRange></bibl>
                    <ab>
                        ወሶበ፡ ተፈጸማ፡ እማንቱ፡ ዓመታት፡ እምፀዐቱ፡ ለአቡ
                        ነ፡ አዳም፡ እምገነት፡ ቀርበ፡ ጊዜ፡ ምጽአቱ፡ ለመድኀኒተ፡ ኵሉ፡ ዓለም፡ ወመድኀ
                        ኒቶሙ፡ እምቅኔሁ፡ ለሰይጣን፡ እስመ፡ ሞኦሙ፡ እስመ፡ አምለኩ፡ ጣዖተ፡ ኀዲጎ
                        ሙ፡ እግዚአብሔርሃ፡ መስተሣህለ።
                    </ab>
